  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka's economic crisis is due to China's debt trap - Taiwan",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "He has stated that China is the cause of Sri Lanka's economic crisis, which has never been seen since Sri Lanka's independence in 1948, and has revealed the results of the debt trap created by China's new Silk Road project.",
        "All 60 Taiwanese nationals in Sri Lanka are safe and every individual who maintains contact with Taiwanese nationals can contact the ministry or the office of the Taiwanese representative, he said."
      ],
